    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Motif comprising a heavy-armed cross with a lighter-armed X-shape over it (that is, an eight-armed figure), with the heavier arms typically terminating in a ram's horn motif.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000132/Suzzallo-UW</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
